item.title: Project 1 (copy)
item.description: Here, the objective is to compare the speed and ease of use with either [Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/berkeleyearth/climate-change-earth-surface-temperature-data), which combines 1.6 billion temperature reports from various datasets such as NOAA’s MLOST, NASA’s GISTEMP and the UK’s HadCrut. All temperatures are in units of **<sup>*o*</sup>*C* and the dataset is roughly 533Mb.
